                                        <div class="exc-title">
                        <h1>Dumbbell Single Arm Tricep Extension</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="social mr-bottom-20">
                        <p class="has-small-font-size pri-color-2" style="margin-bottom: 0">Follow us: </p>
                                                        <a target="_blank" href="#"><img alt="facebook"
                                        src="https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/facebook.svg" /></a>
                                                            <a target="_blank" href="https://www.youtube.com/@workoutendomondo"><img alt="youtube"
                                        src="https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/youtube.svg" /></a>
                                                            <a target="_blank" href="https://www.instagram.com/workoutendomondo/"><img alt="instagram"
                                        src="https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/instagram-2-1.svg" /></a>
                                                            <a target="_blank" href="https://www.pinterest.com/endomondo/"><img alt="pinterest"
                                        src="https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/pinterest-1.svg" /></a>
                                                            <a target="_blank" href="https://www.newsbreak.com/m/endomondo-306392510"><img alt="newsbreak"
                                        src="https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/svgexport-2-2-1.svg" /></a>
                                                </div>
                    <div class="exc-description">
                        <p>Dumbbell single-arm tricep extensions effectively isolate and define the triceps and upper arms. They improve overall muscle strength and stability to encourage upper arm <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6950543/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">hypertrophy</a>.</p><p>Your triceps are crucial for many functional activities involving raising or reaching your arms across the body, pushing, and pulling. Performing<a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/tricep-stretches" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> tricep stretches</a> and exercises helps strengthen these muscles, improving performance in many daily tasks.</p><p>Continue reading for all the details you need to perform dumbbell single-arm tricep extensions, including proper technique, workout structure, and muscle activation.</p>                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
